column1: LEGEND
Wind direction (in degrees clockwise from true north) as reported on the hour
The reading at h00 can either be interpreted as the last reading of the previous day or the first reading of the current day
*** indicates that data is missing or not yet available in the current month
---- indicates that data is unavailable or was not requested
0 indicates calm
The 'mx' column reports the direction of the highest wind gust reported in the 24 hour period.
The 'mxtime' column indicates the time at which the maximum wind gust was reported
The following wind direction ranges are used.
